stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Initialize: Create Server & Observers
    
    Initialize --> CreateAuction: createAuction()
    
    CreateAuction --> RegisterObservers: Auction OPEN
    
    RegisterObservers --> RegisterObservers: attach() observers
    
    RegisterObservers --> Bidding: Ready for bids
    
    Bidding --> ValidateBid: placeBid()
    
    ValidateBid --> NotifyAll: Valid bid - notify all
    ValidateBid --> NotifySingle: Invalid bid - notify one
    
    NotifySingle --> Bidding: Continue
    
    NotifyAll --> UpdateObservers: Observers update
    UpdateObservers --> Bidding: More bids
    UpdateObservers --> Close: closeAuction()
    
    Close --> FinalNotify: Auction CLOSED - notify all
    
    FinalNotify --> [*]: Cleanup
